name: Tendril Cirrus
body:
### Welcome to Cirrus
This project is part of Computer Science Senior Project at the University of Colorado at Boulder.

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Cirrus Team Members

### Support or Contact
Have an issue?  Let us know.
